column4: UPDATE 2-Delphi  Transdev to develop self-driving transport service in Europe
column5: DETROIT  June 7 Delphi Automotive PLC will partner with Paris-based Transdev Group  a public transport service controlled by the French government  to develop an automated on-demand shuttle service in Europe  the companies said on Wednesday.

column4: Blackberry introduces auto software  will bundle with Qualcomm chips
column5: TORONTO  June 7 Blackberry Ltd. said on Wednesday it has developed new software for running complex computer systems on vehicles that will be bundled with semiconductors sold by Qualcomm Inc.
